dialog.body: Hello, thank you for reaching out to Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Ryan Brooks. May I have your name, please?
Nice to meet you, Stephanie. Could you please provide me with your policy number?
Sure, my policy number is eight five zero two one.
Thank you. Additionally, could you confirm your date of birth for verification purposes?
Yes, my date of birth is zero six one nine, nineteen sixty-five.
Great, thank you for providing that information, Stephanie. Is there anything specific I can assist you with today regarding your policy or a claim?
I wanted to add a new vehicle to my policy.
I can help you with that. Please provide me with the make, model, and year of the vehicle you'd like to add.
Thank you for your time, Stephanie. If you have any further questions or need assistance in the future, feel free to reach out. Have a great day!
